The '''Duhma''' were a rare [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Species/Legends|species]] that was divided into many tribes. The tribes identified themselves through use of ceremonial [[Tattoo/Legends|tattoos]]. The Duhma lived on the dark side of their [[Planet/Legends|planet]] and had lost their sight over time. As a result, they wore dark visors during their occasional journeys off their planet to protect their highly sensitive eyes.

[[Abal Karda]] used a visor and Duhma tattoos as a disguise after he was marked as an Enemy of the Empire.

